Univen Campus Navigator
Univen Campus Navigator is a lightweight web-based assistant designed to help students easily navigate the University of Venda campus. The application provides an interactive chat-style interface where users can ask for directions, campus locations, and general navigation assistance in a clean, modern UI.
Features
Chat-based campus navigation interface
Responsive split-view layout for enhanced usability
Smooth animations and modern dark-themed design
Scalable structure ready for backend or AI integration
Mobile-friendly and browser-ready (no installation required)
Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3 (Flexbox, animations, responsive layout)
JavaScript (for chat logic integration â€“ optional extension)
Usage
Download or clone the project files.
Open the index.html file in any modern web browser.
Start interacting with the navigator through the chat interface.
Future Improvements
Integration with live campus maps
AI-powered navigation responses
Real-time building and route search
Backend API connectivity for dynamic data
